\begin_layout Standard
In conclusion, we demonstrate a one point stigmatic Rowland grating WDM
 with 21 channels, 1 nm channel spacing and better than -10 dB crosstalk.
 Since the free spectral range is greater the 100 nm, by adding additional
 output waveguides it is possible to construct a WDM that covers whole C-band.
